(a+b+c)
\begin{align*}\left(x_1+x_2+x_3\right)^2=\sum _{k_1+k_2+k_3=2} \left(\begin{array}{c} 2 \\ k_1,k_2,k_3 \end{array}\right)\prod _{1\leq t\leq n} x_t^{k_t}\end{align*}
(a+b+c)^2
(x_1+x_2+\ldots +x_m)^n=\sum _{k_1+k_2+\ldots +k_m=n} \left(\begin{array}{c} n,  k_1,k_2,\ldots, k_m\end{array}\right)\prod _{1\leq t\leq m} x_t^{k_t}
m=3
(a+b+c)^n=\sum _{k_1+k_2+k_3=n} \left(\begin{array}{c} n,  k_1,k_2, k_3\end{array}\right)a^{k_1}b^{k_2}c^{k_3}
